message:
Joined inauguration of #RailVikasShivir via video conference & spoke on Centre's efforts for transforming railways. 

Central Government is doing everything possible to infuse railways with better technology, innovation & infrastructure required in this century. Our Rail Budgets went beyond political considerations. They were focussed on ushering a paradigm shift in the functioning of the railways.
